  "remarks": "Gachsaran Oil & Gas Company is managed via the National Iranian South Oil Company (NISOC), and it is a subsidiary (100 %) of the State-owned National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). In turn, NIOC provides support to and is owned by the Government of Iran. Therefore, Gachsaran Oil & Gas Company is controlled by an entity providing support to and owned by the Government of Iran.",
